    res = 1
    num = 0
    sign = 1
    stk = []
    for c in expression:
        if c.isdigit():
            num = 10 * num + (ord(c) - ord('0'))
        elif c == '+':
            res += sign * num
            num = 0
            sign = 1
        elif c == '-':
            res += sign * num
            num = 0
            sign = -1
        elif c == '(':
            stk.append(res)
            stk.append(sign)
            res = 0
            sign = 1
        elif c == ')':
            res += sign * num
            res *= stk.pop()
            res += stk.pop()
            num = 0
            sign = 1
    if num:
        res += sign * num
    return res
